<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٢٦٧]</span> ذو النون المصري الزاهد الواعظ <span class="c2">(١)</span>:<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c1">"الفوائد"</span> <span class="c2">(ص ٨٠)</span>: <span class="c1">"ليس بشيء في الرواية"</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[٢٦٨]</span> ذوّاد بن عُلْبة الحارثي أبو المنذر الكوفي <span class="c2">(٢)</span>:<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c1">"التنكيل"</span> <span class="c2">(١/ ١٨٩)</span>: <span class="c1">"ضعيف"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
